Uploader: David Benn, D.Benn@appcomp.utas.edu.au

	Speller - A nice program to help anyone learn how to spell almost
	any word.  Very easy and fun to use!

	This is the second version of Speller and includes two utility
	programs for editing speech strings (SpellEd and SpeechEd - the 
	latter is new this time).

